      <title>前景黯淡之际，交易员将欧洲央行 10 月降息视为主要考量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/traders-bring-ecb-october-rate-cut-into-play-as-outlook-darkens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着经济正在走弱的证据越来越多，交易员们越来越相信欧洲央行下个月将再次降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/traders-bring-ecb-october-rate-cut-into-play-as-outlook-darkens</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 07:06:53 GMT</pubDate>
